        </p>

        <label className="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-fuchsia-600 hover:bg-fuchsia-500 text-white font-bold rounded-full shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(232,121,249,0.3)] cursor-pointer transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" className="h-5 w-5 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
